a real problem.

00:51.501 --> 00:53.634
Oh, shit!

00:53.634 --> 00:55.501
Lou, what's your position?

00:55.501 --> 00:58.067
LOU:
 <i>We're on three. We're in</i>
 <i>the middle of an arson, chief.</i>

