leave those kids.

01:09.701 --> 01:11.167
LOU:
Goddamn door won't shut.

01:11.167 --> 01:12.667
We're sitting
on a powder keg here.

01:12.667 --> 01:15.067
Urgent! Urgent!
The bulkhead is bricked over.

01:15.067 --> 01:17.067
 <i>Sixty-two has no means</i>
 <i>of egress.</i>

01:17.067 --> 01:19.601
SID:
 <i>The structure is</i>
 <i>compromised. It is unstable.</i>

01:19.601 --> 01:22.300
 <i>Get off the goddamn roof now.</i>

01:24.033 --> 01:25.701
Go, Tom! Go!

01:25.701 --> 01:26.701
Sure?

01:26.701 --> 01:29.834
We'll be fine. Trust me.

