Today, we are gathered

04:03.434 --> 04:07.367
together to honor five men.

04:07.367 --> 04:09.067
My men.

04:10.067 --> 04:11.901
My brothers.

04:13.000 --> 04:15.434
Five men
who were given a choice.

04:16.567 --> 04:19.100
To run.

04:19.100 --> 04:22.132
To flee for safe ground.

04:22.132 --> 04:26.367
To seek clean, fresh air.

04:26.367 --> 04:28.534
Or to move deeper.

04:28.534 --> 04:30.801
