Hey, look who it is.
Whoa, now.

16:47.100 --> 16:50.667
Don't worry.
I got it. Uhh.

16:50.667 --> 16:52.434
Ohh, shit.

16:52.434 --> 16:55.767
Yo, man, I don't see
