32:15.734 --> 32:17.300
I'm thinking
of getting cremated.

32:17.300 --> 32:18.767
But the only thing
that bothers me

32:18.767 --> 32:20.400
is I don't really know
what that is.

32:20.400 --> 32:22.567
So, I'm thinking maybe
if I just take a little peek,

32:22.567 --> 32:24.534
I could get some comfort,
you know?

32:24.534 --> 32:25.868
You're not opening the box.

32:25.868 --> 32:27.567
Why not?
Because I just said.

32:27.567 --> 32:30.367
It's my best friend in there
and your superior officer, okay?

32:30.367 --> 32:32.200
I don't want you
poking around in the ashes

32:32.200 --> 32:34.100
like it's some kind of
Zen garden

32:34.100 --> 32:35.467
with a little rake or something.

32:35.467 --> 32:37.300
[FRANCO CHUCKLES]

32:45.534 --> 32:47.234
All right, enough with the gum!

32:48.434 --> 32:49.434
Spit it out!

32:49.434 --> 32:50.767
Fine!

32:50.767 --> 32:52.534
Fine!

32:54.434 --> 32:55.634
[ALL YELLING INDISTINCTLY

32:55.634 --> 32:56.968
FRANCO:
Oh, my God.

32:56.968 --> 32:58.434
[COUGHING]

32:58.434 --> 32:59.434
God.

32:59.434 --> 33:01.434
[ALL COUGHING]

33:04.634 --> 33:06.067
Oh, my God.

33:06.067 --> 33:08.167
It's like Lou-Maggedon.

33:08.167 --> 33:10.267
Guys, come over by the box.
Get it into the box.

33:10.267 --> 33:13.567
God, this is disgusting.
I'm covered in Lou.

33:13.567 --> 33:14.734
I got Lou up my nose.

33:14.734 --> 33:16.200
I definitely swallowed
some Lou.

33:16.200 --> 33:18.400
That's nothing.
I got half a pound of Lou

33:18.400 --> 33:19.834
down my ass crack.

33:19.834 --> 33:21.968
I thought I shit myself
when that thing blew.

33:21.968 --> 33:23.267
Now I'm pretty sure it's Lou.

33:23.267 --> 33:24.968
Either that
or a Lou-shit combination.

33:24.968 --> 33:27.133
You had to open the box.

33:27.133 --> 33:28.634
Ah, it's not just my fault.

33:28.634 --> 33:31.234
