TOMMY:
All right, everybody.

44:10.267 --> 44:12.501
Home sweet home.

44:13.634 --> 44:16.534
So, what do you think, uh,
pizza?

44:16.534 --> 44:20.300
Yeah. Pineapple pizza.
Pineapple?

44:20.300 --> 44:23.367
COLLEEN:
Yeah. It's her new thing.
Hawaiian-style.

44:23.367 --> 44:25.667
There's a place
that has it down the street.

44:25.667 --> 44:27.767
Damn, what's next,
orange pizza?

44:27.767 --> 44:29.734
They have a citrus one.

44:29.734 --> 44:31.100
Lemon
and lemon-pomegranate.

44:31.100 --> 44:32.734
SHAWN:
Pomegranate?

44:32.734 --> 44:35.200
Who the hell's
making these pies,
Ricky Goddamn Martin?

44:35.200 --> 44:36.234
[CHUCKLES]

44:36.234 --> 44:37.434
COLLEEN:
I want pepperoni.

44:37.434 --> 44:39.067
Pepperoni!

44:39.067 --> 44:41.334
That's my girl.
Keeping it old-school.

44:41.334 --> 44:42.601
That's why I love you.

44:42.601 --> 44:44.467
Well, I'm starved.
So, what do we have to do?

44:44.467 --> 44:46.467
We call it in,
or we gotta go down and get it?

44:46.467 --> 44:47.501
JANET:
Tommy?

44:47.501 --> 44:49.000
Yeah, honey, I know.
Extra cheese.

44:49.000 --> 44:50.334
She wants extra cheese.

44:50.334 --> 44:52.901
I don't think they make
a Twizzler pizza yet, hon.

44:52.901 --> 44:54.634
Gross.
JANET: Tommy?

44:54.634 --> 44:56.634
Yeah, hon?
JANET: Yeah, I need you

44:56.634 --> 44:57.901
to come in here now please.

44:57.901 --> 44:59.000
Yeah, hon.

44:59.000 --> 45:00.000
I need the number.

45:00.000 --> 45:01.100
Colleen's got it.

45:01.100 --> 45:02.100
[GROANS]

45:02.100 --> 45:03.934
What's going on?

45:03.934 --> 45:05.667
Ooh.

45:05.667 --> 45:06.767
You don't want pizza.

45:08.400 --> 45:10.634
I'm having the baby.

45:10.634 --> 45:14.400
O-o-okay, do you think
that you have the strength

45:14.400 --> 45:16.834
to make it down
to the truck?

45:16.834 --> 45:19.334
Tommy, I'm having
the baby now.

45:19.334 --> 45:20.434
Are you sure?

45:21.400 --> 45:22.667
Why don't you lift up
my skirt

45:22.667 --> 45:24.667
and ask the baby
yourself?

45:24.667 --> 45:25.734
Ugh!
Oh, my God!

45:25.734 --> 45:27.300
Oh, my God!

45:27.300 --> 45:28.834
Oh, my God!

45:28.834 --> 45:30.367
[INDISTINCT CHATTERING]

45:30.367 --> 45:31.567
Oh, shit!
Oh, shit!

45:31.567 --> 45:33.734
All right! Relax!

45:33.734 --> 45:35.133
You know,
them I can understand.

45:35.133 --> 45:37.234
But you, you're
a firefighter. Okay?

45:37.234 --> 45:38.801
That's not it, Tom.
It's just that

45:38.801 --> 45:40.901
I'm gonna have to deliver
my wife's mama's baby.

45:40.901 --> 45:42.501
You ain't doing it,
okay.

45:42.501 --> 45:44.667
Because you're gonna pass out
in two seconds.

45:44.667 --> 45:47.434
[INDISTINCT CHATTERING]

45:47.434 --> 45:49.200
Everybody shut up!

45:49.200 --> 45:51.634
Okay?
I am not gonna pass out!

45:52.901 --> 45:54.133
This is what I need,
okay?

45:54.133 --> 45:56.267
Colleen, get me a giant
pot of water,

45:56.267 --> 45:58.133
and boil it.
Okay.

45:58.133 --> 46:00.400
You're gonna get me a pair
of scissors. All right, go.

46:00.400 --> 46:01.901
Katy, get me some towels.
Towels.

46:01.901 --> 46:03.200
While you're
in the bathroom,

46:03.200 --> 46:04.200
my toolbox
is in there.

46:04.200 --> 46:05.868
Get a ball of string
out of it.

46:05.868 --> 46:07.934
Cut off a couple of long pieces
of string.

46:07.934 --> 46:09.567
Put the string
and the scissors

46:09.567 --> 46:12.100
into the boiling water.
Okay, honey, here we go.

46:12.100 --> 46:13.968
Okay, just...down here.
[GROANS]

46:13.968 --> 46:15.501
Oh, God.

46:15.501 --> 46:18.467
Hang on. All right,
is that good? Good?

46:18.467 --> 46:20.200
[GROWLS]

46:20.200 --> 46:22.067
Move back, okay.
Got it. Back up.

46:22.067 --> 46:25.434
Further.
Leave the room?

46:25.434 --> 46:26.634
Stay?

46:26.634 --> 46:28.567
[GRUNTING]

46:28.567 --> 46:30.968
Stop talking!
Okay.

46:30.968 --> 46:33.534
Shh! Got it.

46:34.901 --> 46:36.100
Holy shit!

46:36.100 --> 46:37.501
I'm gonna need
a catcher's mitt.

46:37.501 --> 46:38.734
This is happening right now.

46:38.734 --> 46:41.434
Kids, get in here.
Everybody get in here.

46:41.434 --> 46:43.234
Here we go.

46:43.234 --> 46:45.434
COLLEEN: Mom, are you--?
SHAWN: Whoa! Shit!

46:45.434 --> 46:47.167
[YELLS]
TOMMY: Here we go.

46:47.167 --> 46:49.534
All right, honey. Just give
me a couple of quick pushes.

46:49.534 --> 46:51.334
Holy shit,
it's coming!

46:51.334 --> 46:54.634
Stop saying "shit."
Okay, stop saying "shit."

46:54.634 --> 46:56.367
Holy shit!
TOMMY: Here it comes.

46:56.367 --> 46:58.167
